---
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 sm:py-28 px-6 relative">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="section-label" data-animate>
      <span class="section-number">01</span>
      <span class="section-line"></span>
      <span class="section-label-text">About</span>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-start mt-4">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-5" data-animate data-delay="100">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-center sm:text-left">
          I build products that solve <span class="gradient-text">real operational problems</span>.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg text-center sm:text-left">
          I’m a product leader with 13+ years across hardware, software, workflow, and connected products. My work usually sits where customer pain, business priorities, and execution all meet.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg text-center sm:text-left">
          That has meant portfolios totaling $275M, revenue growth up to 385%, and products spanning apps, portals, CRM and workflow systems, eCommerce tools, and connected hardware.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg text-center sm:text-left">
          I’m most useful when the work is messy, cross-functional, and important. I’m also still building, through products like DojoGate, ShieldRA, and DocHaven.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo + stats -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col items-center gap-6 sm:gap-8" data-animate data-delay="200">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="relative w-44 h-44 sm:w-56 sm:h-56">
          <div class="photo-glow"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 border-border z-10">
            <img 
              src="/images/bibek.jpg" 
              alt="Bibek Ghimire" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <svg class="absolute inset-[-12px] w-[calc(100%+24px)] h-[calc(100%+24px)]" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="96" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 6" style="animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;" />
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 sm:gap-4 w-full">
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="stat-number text-xl sm:text-2xl" data-count="13" data-suffix="+">0</span>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-[10px] sm:text-xs mt-1">Years Exp.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="stat-number text-xl sm:text-2xl" data-count="275" data-suffix="M">0</span>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-[10px] sm:text-xs mt-1">Portfolio Managed</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="stat-number text-xl sm:text-2xl" data-count="385" data-suffix="%">0</span>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-[10px] sm:text-xs mt-1">Rev. Scaled</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick facts card -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 w-full space-y-3">
          <div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-mono">Education</p>
            <p class="text-text-primary text-sm font-medium mt-1">B.S. Aerospace & Mechanical Eng.</p>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-xs">Oklahoma State University, 2009–2012</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-border pt-3">
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-mono">Industries</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-1">
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-accent-subtle text-accent border border-accent/20">Automation</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-accent-subtle text-accent border border-accent/20">HVAC/Energy</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-accent-subtle text-accent border border-accent/20">Oil & Gas</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-accent-subtle text-accent border border-accent/20">SaaS / AI</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-accent-subtle text-accent border border-accent/20">Defense & Aerospace</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
